This localconf file is what i used for my first build with the Yocto Project ( http://yoctoproject.org ).

This configuration file shall only work, if you hava a certain directory structure.

THIS SHALL NOT WORK UNDER NEWBIE CONFIGURATION.

The changes are bare minimal, to ensure that a new build shall not be required anytime, the layered architecture of
Yocto makes it even more smooth.


Changes: 
	1. Download directory has been changed.
	2. Number of tasks
	3. Number of Parallel makes
	4. Sstate-cache directory
	5. File mirror.

All these changes have been documented in the configuration files too.
